items.sentence: Let me tell you something that you don't know.
Tom doesn't know where his French textbook is.
Tom didn't tell us when he planned to do that.
Tom didn't tell me when he planned to do that.
Tom didn't know either Mary or John back then.
Tom didn't expect Mary to be such a good cook.
Tom crashed his car a week after he bought it.
Tom asked the same question to several people.
Tom asked me how much money I had in the bank.
Tom asked Mary to pick John up at the airport.
